metadata.name: Roulette
metadata.description:
So, here it is… a thought provoking collection that might raise some eyebrows but a collection that speaks volumes to me.  
Each ‘Mental Health Day’ (MHday) piece tells its own story and is created with some of my past experiences in ‘mind’.  
With a newly found passion for digital art, a former Telco specialist and wood crafts person, I have been struggling with mental health for most of my life, I have only in recent years discovered some explanations.  
The MHday collection will be a continuous project for me and will be added to on regular basis.  
Thanks to the NFT community and all the great artists out there, you are a great inspiration to me as I venture further into the world of NFT’s and digital art.
